Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:24.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:30.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:42.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.14,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.18,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:00.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:13.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.48,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:28.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:24.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜欢着紧张的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:30.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}兴奋起来走向更广阔的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:42.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只专注于眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁都无法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.18,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连同那份泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部开始闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:00.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:13.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.48,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:28.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没有进行晨练了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直在参加部团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是大赛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以往一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好  已经全部康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:41.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第22话\N败者与胜者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！面！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周末就是关东大赛了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是很了不起的大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东地区的水平和中国地区完全不是一个层次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在上面取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们部的强劲也自然能成为焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一定能让他收回解雇的成名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小珠的呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…从小聪莉那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下了一本！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精彩！宫崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强哦  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续！聪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我还没有忘记刚才的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能输呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定行！这次一定行啊！老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗  那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么  继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东大赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真让人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠最近变强了  更重要的是变精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  果然参加部团活动是对的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  和同龄人一起练习是一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  在这个时候  布雷巴出现…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小珠救了出来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都记住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…铃木同学也会参加关东大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  这次的大赛对大家来说会是一个大活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得太有部团的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而会让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好比「如果只有我输了怎么办呢」之类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  勇次君很强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样明天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢  这才开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊  段君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不碰遥控器一个小时就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个周末就是大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦死了  谁会去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就不参加社团活动了  拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大赛前我先这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们蛮强的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「蛮」…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话你就下个定论嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能下定论的只有小珠一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得自己「蛮强」就自满起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转眼就会被别人追过去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说  我怎么觉得他两眼就盯着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…那个嘛  不能粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有干劲的话一定会输掉比赛的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样都会输吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要我怎么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  换人换人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉红
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是室江高剑道部的证明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是部长！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这就是胜利的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高！Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次参加这样气氛的大赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和以前的比赛是绝对不一样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在这里打赢才是真材实料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还用那种回转寿司打发我可绝对说不过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回转寿司？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  你们来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次合宿后就没见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们可是绝好状态哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你切什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过出赛表了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要碰面的话就在决赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的团体战  要决胜负就在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是大家都能赢到决赛才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说什么不明不白的话  你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将！在这里别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们参加多少比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团体战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赢四场是不能到决赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度对现在的我们来说轻而易举啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决战  在明天的个人战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种热血…让人想起了过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在决胜战碰面吧  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目标也是那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再赢一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然练习剑道的人逐渐减少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但充满热情的诸位仍然聚集在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个退居二线的人感到非常欣慰并对你们充满期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}凛就在这些人里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可以说在你们其中将会出现把全新的剑道推向社会的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在第五十五会关东高中生剑道大赛开赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道之神…是存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第几个出场？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次峰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  今天就做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是还觉得她是以前的宫崎同学  小心吃苦头！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不好意思  我也不是以前的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法超越我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过二刀流在高中生正式战不能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么想的呢  凯莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！小聪莉干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你有什么招数
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～赶上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都帮你拍下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效  比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一把刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样就出现可能性了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之是一刀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是二刀流很复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我输在这里  就没有练剑道的意义了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退开！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学！好好注意前方！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用二刀流的话  一刀又怎么会弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仍不及我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜呢  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就能赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  都是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赢哦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三回战出线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她们是真的想和你们打嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是场好比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎欢迎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经把小都都的份一起弥补完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠和东就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果纪梨乃和小鞘能赢的话  就真的能进决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你光这么一厢情愿地想的话  小心摔了跟头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看对战表了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来就轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛是秀玉高的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是赢不过施奈德的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么赢不过的原因  我今天就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…我认识的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没钱啦  走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再杀会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啥  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴你干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火了？不就是个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们够了  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用他们续币
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先锋虽然赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但次锋和中坚都败下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦战中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个次峰基本上都不带动的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像室江高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她做大将的话  没可能输的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃！拜托了！给小珠个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  来加油吧  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下局小都都也会复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要赢！拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子下来就有机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就拜托咯  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真险呐  对方好强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  毕竟接下来是小珠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下局换下次序好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让宫崎同学做前锋比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙开始动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等比赛结束后说说她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上段？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个时候一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会输？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  振作！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在比赛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单手面？从上段？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还拿下了一本…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…好强！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那是弱点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  安藤同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要拿下一局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要赢！我要赢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是正义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  会输就是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是正义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要拿下一局  拿下一局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以对她用…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白方  秀玉高获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小岛田礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然今天小都输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但消沉的小都对礼美来说也一样OK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气的小都  凶暴的小都  微笑的小都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发怒的小都  睡着的小都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚尖踢到了衣柜角跳起来的小都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个都无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.82,0:24:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回「谎言与沉默」会看到什么样的小都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～只是想像的话就…（喷）
